ğŸ’¡ What Happens When You Ask a Question
It reads your custom rules and decides how to respond.


If unsure, it checks your uploaded file (truth-guidelines.txt) for guidance.

It runs a live web search to find credible, up-to-date sources.

It cross-checks the information and only replies when it can verify each claim.



